Title: Inpage search: Allow searching for folders on hosts page
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1696575294
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.3.0b1

Until now, it was only possible to search for hosts on the "Setup" - "Hosts"
page. The inpage search in the page menu now also allows searching for folders.

